nodes.text: Gort's was a Mon Calamari restaurant in the Blackpit Slums that served food from Dac, and had a sulyet bar where sulyet was served fresh. Some of the cuisine served was tikit grain, grain ball with a nudibranch, grain wine, and nexufish. Located on the fiftieth level, Gort's featured Quarren music, which was mostly atonal quetarra études, and had a varied clientele.
